 *
 * Arguments:
 * - seconds_per_tick: The amount of time that has elapsed since the last tick.
 * - times_fired: The number of times SSmobs has ticked.
 */
/mob/living/carbon/proc/handle_dead_metabolization(seconds_per_tick, times_fired)
